descriptionHtml:
Hello Nexus! This is my first upload so I may be a little rusty with the description.


Any Redguard players out there looking for a beautiful, charming and sexy female character to play with? Oh, to play Skyrim that is... ahem.

Anyways, I bring you Laraya. She\'s been my main character for quite some time and today I felt like sharing a level 1, Helgen Keep savegame of her.
I\'m quite proud of her looks and I think that she deserves a place on the Nexus.


You\'ll need the following mods if you want Laraya to look like in the screenshots:

Required mods:
ApachiiSkyHair 1.4 Full + ApachiiHairFemale v1.0 & ApachiiSkyHair UNP, CBBE BodySize Patch: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168
Inhabitants of Skyrim (TOP Main File): http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18820
High Quality Eyes (Non DD version): http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/498
Covewomen (Look #3): http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3563 

Recommended Mods:
Caliente\'s Female Body Mod BBE v3.1 (Curvy): http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2666
Caliente\'s Vanilla Armors - Combined Pack & Caliente\\\'s Vanilla Armors - Soldier Pack: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/12273
Better standing animation (Style 1): http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/18981


Want her as a follower? Then go [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26350][b]here[/b][/url] and grab her!


Credits to:
Apachii for the best hairstyle mod on the Nexus!
Rops1981 for the awesome character presets!
Xenius for the awesome looking eyes!
mrLenski for making the females of Skyrim beatiful!
Caliente for providing IMO the best body mod!
Kybou for the lovely idle animation for female characters!
